<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب وح:</span> <span class="c2">(أَبَاحَهُ)</span> الشَّيْءَ أَحَلَّهُ لَهُ وَ <span class="c2">(الْمُبَاحُ)</span> ضِدُّ الْمَحْظُورِ وَ <span class="c2">(اسْتَبَاحَهُ)</span> اسْتَأْصَلَهُ وَ <span class="c2">(بَاحَ)</span> بِسِرِّهِ أَظْهَرَهُ وَبَابُهُ قَالَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>